    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE NEW SECTION 97-45-35, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CREATE THE OFFENSE OF FINANCIAL INSTITUTION ACCOUNTS FRAUD; TO PROVIDE CRIMINAL PENALTIES ON A SCALE CORRESPONDING TO THE TOTAL VALUE OF THE MONEY, PROPERTY, SERVICES, OR OTHER THING OF VALUE OBTAINED OR SOUGHT TO BE OBTAINED; TO PROVIDE FOR THE VENUE OF THE CRIME; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
